---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Knowledge Hub 2025 — Minimizing Litigation Risk">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">2025 Event</span>
      <h1>Minimizing Litigation Risk</h1>
      <p>Expert insights on protecting nonprofit organizations from litigation risk, covering key areas of vulnerability and practical prevention strategies.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-grid">
      <div class="content-main">
        <h2>About This Session</h2>
        <p>Taras Kulish of Mills &amp; Mills LLP delivered a comprehensive presentation on how not-for-profit organizations can identify, manage, and minimize their exposure to litigation risk. The session covered common legal pitfalls, director liability, employment disputes, and practical steps boards can take to protect their organizations.</p>

        <h2>Key Topics</h2>
        <ul class="topics-list">
          <li>Understanding litigation risk in the not-for-profit context</li>
          <li>Director and officer liability</li>
          <li>Employment and volunteer relationship management</li>
          <li>Insurance and risk mitigation strategies</li>
          <li>Best practices for corporate governance and documentation</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Speaker</h2>
        <div class="speaker-block">
          <div class="speaker-avatar"><span>TK</span></div>
          <div>
            <strong>Taras Kulish</strong>
            <p>Business &amp; Not-for-Profit Counsel, <a href="https://www.millsandmills.ca/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mills &amp; Mills LLP</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="article-link">
          <a href="https://www.millsandmills.ca/community/minimizing-litigation-risk-insights-from-taras-kulish-at-knowledge-hub-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary">Read the full article on Mills &amp; Mills &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="content-aside">
        <div class="info-block">
          <dl>
            <dt>Date</dt>
            <dd>April 2025</dd>
            <dt>Location</dt>
            <dd>The Old Mill, Toronto</dd>
            <dt>Format</dt>
            <dd>In-person &amp; livestream</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>
        <a href="/past-events" class="back-link">&larr; All past events</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--sp-8) 0;
  }
  .page-hero .eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: var(--sp-3); }
  .page-hero h1 { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: var(--sp-3); }
  .page-hero p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.6; }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: var(--sp-8);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .content-main h2 { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: var(--sp-3); }
  .content-main h2:not(:first-child) { margin-top: var(--sp-7); }
  .content-main p { font-size: 15.5px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; max-width: 600px; }

  .topics-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .topics-list li {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding-left: var(--sp-4);
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .topics-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 9px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  .speaker-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .speaker-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--surface);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .speaker-block strong { font-size: 15px; color: var(--navy); }
  .speaker-block p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 2px; }

  .article-link { margin-top: var(--sp-7); }

  .content-aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }
  .back-link {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .content-aside { position: static; }
  }
</style>
